casebody.data:
Wednesday, June 11, 1997

MOTION DOCKET

94-1143. State v. Robinette.

Montgomery App. No. 14074. The cause is pending in this court on remand from the Supreme Court of the United States.

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that the Clerk shall issue an order for the transmittal of the record from the Court of Appeals for Montgomery County.
